	i can split certain features off into their own branch

How do the diagrams help you visualize the branch structure?
	easier to notice branches and how there's no connection to commits from other branches

What is the result of merging two branches together? Why do we represent it in the diagram the way we do?
	master incorporates the history of both branches into the same master branch

